# Agricultural Commodity Price Forecaster (SDG 2: Zero Hunger)

Machine learning project that forecasts future agricultural commodity prices (rice, wheat, maize) using:
- historical market prices,
- weather signals (temperature, rainfall, humidity),
- seasonal time features.

Goal: help farmers and agri stakeholders decide better crop selling windows.

